f="http://scholar.google.com/citations?view_op=top_venues&amp;hl=en&amp;vq=soc_technologylaw" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">RIPL as the 11<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;most cited technology law journal</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">.&nbsp; While RIPL takes pride in each and every article published,&nbsp;</span><a href="http://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&amp;vq=soc_technologylaw&amp;view_op=list_hcore&amp;venue=bIQhgiGy4DIJ.20121115" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">these are the specific articles</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;that helped RIPL achieve such a high ranking.&nbsp; Google Scholar Metrics cover articles published during the 2007 to 2011 time period and are based on citations from all articles indexed by Google Scholar as of November 15th, 2012.&nbsp; This success, in addition to being cited in a recent petition for writ of certiorari, is a testament to the hard work and dedication RIPL Executive Board members put into the Review.</span>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 28 Nov 2012 22:55:28 -0600";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:24:"\n			\n			\n			\n\n			\n			\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"RIPL Cited in Petition for Cert to the Supreme Court";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_l