er Plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"http://www.slidedeck.com/?p=12690";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:326:"Were excited to announce that SlideDeck is now a featured plugin for SiteGround Hosting WordPress users. What does this mean exactly? Now SiteGround users will be able to quickly and easily add SlideDeck to their default WordPress installations with a couple of clicks. SiteGround customers get easy access to SlideDeck,...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Morgan";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3808:"<p>Were excited to announce that SlideDeck is now a featured plugin for SiteGround Hosting WordPress users. What does this mean exactly? Now SiteGround users will be able to quickly and easily add SlideDeck to their default WordPress installations with a couple of clicks. SiteGround customers get easy access to SlideDeck, and of course we get to introduce ourselves to a bunch of new WordPress site owners.</p>\n<p>Why <a href="http://www.siteground.com/index.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e">SiteGround hosting</a> you ask? Because theyre good people, and working with friendly people is one of our top priorities. Plus they offer solid <a href="http://www.siteground.com/wordpress-hosting.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e">hosting for WordPress</a> (among others) and have some unique features that are wins for any site owner:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir="ltr">Unique server security that keeps hacks isolated to affected accounts</li>\n<li dir="ltr">Automatic updates to the latest WordPress versions</li>\n<li dir="ltr">In-house created WordPress caching plugin (3 caching layers!)</li>\n<li dir="ltr">Cloudflare CDN integration</li>\n<li dir="ltr">Security monitoring and rapid upgrades</li>\n<li dir="ltr">Across the board hardware updates</li>\n<li dir="ltr">Multiple hosting packages that start as low as $3.95/month</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also love that theyve <a href="http://blog.siteground.com/coolest-feature/">outlined their most popular features in infographics</a>. Much more enjoyable than lots of technical documents, PDFs and bulleted feature lists.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.morganbrown.co/">Morgan</a> setup a new blog over on SiteGround after <a href="http://www.siteground.com/index.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e">checking them out</a>. You might want to keep them in mind the next time youre looking for hosting, too.</p>\n<p>Stay tuned for more news from SlideDeck. Were just getting started.<strong id="internal-source-marker_0.6110795175191015"> </strong></p>\n<h3>SiteGround&#8217;s Unique WordPress Caching</h3>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.siteground.com/wordpress-hosting.htm?afcode=419559cef569bdfec620acbf1d67a05e"><img class="aligncenter" title="Siteground WordPress Caching" src="http://www.siteground.com/fw/img/infographic_supercacherspeed.jpg" alt="Siteground WordPress Caching" width="560" height="3320" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg?bafc15" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=RH0UOvy14gs:Dt4-ic8kWIw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="