ognized IP program. Many RIPL students possess a technical background  with degrees ranging from bachelors of science to PhDs  and have experience in all facets of intellectual property. These students provide authors with quality editorial assistance, such as conducting research, adding footnotes to expand legal discussions, and perfecting citations. Further, RIPL is willing to convert a transcribed speech into a publishable article. RIPLs editorial staff looks forward to working with you in the future.', 'Submit', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-9', '', '', '2013-07-10 16:24:22', '2013-07-10 21:24:22', '', 21, 'http://localhost/riplblog/2013/07/10/21-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
